title: Author and Entrepreneur Gary Vaynerchuk | The Cain Conversat

Gary Vaynerchuk is an entrepreneur and best-selling author of "Jab, Jab, Jab Right-Hook," specializing in social media and marketing. Here he talks to Will Cain for "The Cain Conversation": a look at patience, capitalism, the future and more.
